Let's see how #rstats handles this.

> z <- as.POSIXct("2021-04-04 2:15:00 AM")

> z
[1] "2021-04-04 02:15:00 NZDT"
 
Fair enough that was ambiguous.

> z + 3600
[1] "2021-04-04 02:15:00 NZST"

Okay makes sense.

> z + lubridate::hours(1)
[1] "2021-04-04 03:15:00 NZST"

Oh no.
